OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778533866
OL,3,CFour Cabinet ministers tell Starmer to
OL,4,Cset out resignation timetable
OL,6,FFour ministers, led by the Home
OL,7,FSecretary, have gone into Number 10 to
OL,8,Ftell the prime minister to set out a
OL,9,Ftimetable for him to resign, ITV News
OL,10,Funderstands.
OL,12,FIt comes after four government aides
OL,13,Fhave resigned as they joined dozens of
OL,14,FLabour MPs calling for Sir Keir
OL,15,FStarmer to stand down following a
OL,16,Fdisastrous set of local election
OL,17,Fresults.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
