OL,3,CFour Cabinet ministers tell Starmer to
OL,4,Cset out resignation timetable
OL,6,FITV News has spoken to and tracked
OL,7,Fonline 56 MPs who think the prime
OL,8,Fminister should immediately set out a
OL,9,Ftimeline for his departure - and a
OL,10,Ffurther eight who believe he should
OL,11,Fleave if things do not improve.
OL,13,FStarmer sought to face down critics on
OL,14,FMonday with a promise to prove his
OL,15,Fdoubters wrong, as former minister
OL,16,FCatherine West withdrew threats to
OL,17,Fimminently launch a leadership
OL,18,Fchallenge.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778533866
OL,3,CFour Cabinet ministers tell Starmer to
OL,4,Cset out resignation timetable
OL,6,FBut his speech failed to quell demands
OL,7,Fthat he quit or set out a timetable
OL,8,Ffor his departure from discontented
OL,9,Fbackbenchers, who numbered 61 by
OL,10,FMonday evening.
OL,12,FWest had previously said she would
OL,13,Fchallenge Starmer for the party
OL,14,Fleadership as early as Monday
OL,15,Fafternoon, in an attempt to force the
OL,16,FCabinet to put forward a replacement
OL,17,Fas prime minister.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
