PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778533866
OL,3,CFour Cabinet ministers tell Starmer to
OL,4,Cset out resignation timetable
OL,6,FAfter Starmer insisted he would not
OL,7,F"walk away", the former Foreign Office
OL,8,Fminister said she would now canvass
OL,9,Fsupport within the party for the prime
OL,10,Fminister to set out a timetable for
OL,11,Fhis resignation by September.
OL,13,FSpeculation about the prime minister's
OL,14,Ffuture has intensified since
OL,15,FThursday's elections, in which Labour
OL,16,Flost almost 1,500 English councillors,
OL,17,Fwent backwards in Scotland and slumped
OL,18,Fto third in Wales.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
