OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778533866
OL,3,CFour Cabinet ministers tell Starmer to
OL,4,Cset out resignation timetable
OL,6,FIn a speech in central London on
OL,7,FMonday, Starmer said he took
OL,8,F"responsibility" for the losses but
OL,9,Fwould fight on.
OL,11,FMonday's address had been billed as a
OL,12,Fmove to set out sweeping changes
OL,13,Fneeded to tackle the "big challenges"
OL,14,Ffacing Britain, and was widely seen as
OL,15,Fa "make-or-break" moment for the prime
OL,16,Fminister.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@PO]uD@VOUuD@eO]wD@COUwD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778533866
OL,3,CFour Cabinet ministers tell Starmer to
OL,4,Cset out resignation timetable
OL,6,FHe set out several measures, including
OL,7,Flegislation to nationalise British
OL,8,FSteel, a ban on "far-right agitators"
OL,9,Fcoming to the UK for a planned march
OL,10,Fon Saturday and a plan to put the UK
OL,11,F"at the heart of Europe".
OL,13,FStarmer cast the current political
OL,14,Fmoment as a "battle for the soul" of
OL,15,Fthe UK, warning that if Labour failed,
OL,16,Fthe country would head down "a very
OL,17,Fdark path".
OL,26,@pD@QOUpD@eO]sD@AOUsD@XO]vD@MOUvD@aO]xD@
OL,26,A]OUyD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
