SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778533866
OL,3,CFour Cabinet ministers tell Starmer to
OL,4,Cset out resignation timetable
OL,6,FNorth Northumberland MP David Smith,
OL,7,Fwho has been the UK's special envoy
OL,8,Ffor freedom of religion or belief
OL,9,Fsince 2024, said Labour owed "a debt
OL,10,Fof gratitude" to Starmer but he could
OL,11,Fnot "carry on with the approach we
OL,12,Fhave taken" since the general election.
