PN,30313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778533866
OL,3,CFour Cabinet ministers tell Starmer to
OL,4,Cset out resignation timetable
OL,6,FBlue Labour, an internal pressure
OL,7,Fgroup founded by Labour peer Lord
OL,8,FMaurice Glasman, also called on Monday
OL,9,Ffor the prime minister to set out a
OL,10,Ftimetable for his departure.
OL,12,FOthers have looked towards Greater
OL,13,FManchester Mayor Andy Burnham, saying
OL,14,Fhe should be allowed to return to
OL,15,FParliament.
OL,17,FBut Starmer would not be drawn on
OL,18,Fwhether he would support Burnham's
OL,19,Freturn to Westminster, saying it was a
OL,20,Fmatter for Labour's national executive
OL,21,Fcommittee (NEC).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30314
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778533866
OL,3,CFour Cabinet ministers tell Starmer to
OL,4,Cset out resignation timetable
OL,6,FThe NEC, dominated by supporters of
OL,7,Fthe prime minister, blocked Burnham
OL,8,Ffrom contesting the Gorton and Denton
OL,9,Fby-election earlier this year, and the
OL,10,Fformerly safe Labour seat was won by
OL,11,Fthe Greens.
OL,13,FIn a speech to the Communication
OL,14,FWorkers Union on Monday, former deputy
OL,15,Fprime minister Angela Rayner ` herself
OL,16,Fregarded as a potential leadership
OL,17,Fcontender ` said the decision to block
OL,18,FBurnham should be "put right".
OL,26,@zD@SOUzD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30315
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778533866
OL,3,CFour Cabinet ministers tell Starmer to
OL,4,Cset out resignation timetable
OL,6,FBurnham is yet to comment publicly on
OL,7,Freports that he intends to attempt a
OL,8,Freturn to Westminster, and has pulled
OL,9,Fout of an event at which he was due to
OL,10,Fspeak on Tuesday.
OL,12,FA Survation poll for Compass,
OL,13,Fconducted before the local elections,
OL,14,Ffound 55% of the British public think
OL,15,FStarmer should stand down, and 22%
OL,16,Fthink he can turn things around.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
