FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30316
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778533866
OL,3,CFour Cabinet ministers tell Starmer to
OL,4,Cset out resignation timetable
OL,6,FResponding to the speech, Conservative
OL,7,Fleader Kemi Badenoch said it was "sad
OL,8,Fto watch", adding: "With so many
OL,9,Fresets, even his reset button needs a
OL,10,Freset.
OL,12,F"But I do not take pleasure in
OL,13,Fwatching the prime minister flounder.
OL,15,F"The country needs leadership, not
OL,16,Fanother speech from a man who clearly
OL,17,Fknows something has gone badly wrong,
OL,18,Fbut still can't explain why."
OL,26,@oD@bOUpD@IO]pD@TOUtD@AOUwD@AOUzD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/17
