CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778533866
OL,3,CFour Cabinet ministers tell Starmer to
OL,4,Cset out resignation timetable
OL,6,FBadenoch also dismissed Labour's
OL,7,F"pretenders jostling for his job",
OL,8,Fsaying: "They are busy arguing over
OL,9,Fwho should drive the car, but the
OL,10,Ftruth is they are all heading in the
OL,11,Fwrong direction. They have no vision
OL,12,Ffor the future."
